title: Rolling Sun (2015) - SKIDROW
description:
Rolling Sun (2015) - SKIDROW

* Install using 'Setup.exe'

* Copy/Replace contents of SKIDROW folder to appropriate places in your installation folder.

* use WASD to move, SPACE to jump
  (game neglects to give you these facts)

* Game generates x86 and x64 shortcuts, choose what you need

* No virus in this copy, I played it 3 minutes before I felt like shooting myself for some fun
